Trichet Says Not Appropriate for ECB to Leverage the EFSF

-- B y   J a n a   R a n d o w
-- 
2011-10-06T13:05:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-06/trichet-says-not-appropriate-for-ecb-to-leverage-the-efsf.html
European Central Bank President Jean-
Claude Trichet said it’s not appropriate for the ECB to leverage
 Europe ’s rescue fund.  “The governments have the capacity to leverage,” the
European Financial Stability Facility, Trichet said at a press
conference in Berlin today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jana Randow in Frankfurt at 
